Copy all PHP files to proper location
You have to choice "Thread Safety Enable" version of PHP

Copy this files and folder to new PHP location
	- php.ini
	- phpForApache.ini
	- wampserver
	- zend_ext
	
Change "extension_dir" locations in "php.ini" and "phpForApache.ini" to new location

Download new php_xdebud.dll file for your new php version

Copy it to zend_ext folder

Change "php_xdebud.dll" file with the new one.
You can download .dll files in here: https://xdebug.org/files/

Restart wamp and select your new php version
